desc=I am so busy lately because of the Lava Plateau. If I complete a request, the next one is just around the corner. I am going to die of overwork, if it goes on like this. 

 The request this time is from the Noble Masquer. We were asked to bring horns of the horn spider after hunting them down. They want to use it for their experiments. Probaly they have lots of work to do and requests, too. They are so great. 

 If you get the horn, just give it to Miss Lizzie directly. Then go ahead. 
runDlg=Will you finish that work quickly and help me out?
finishDlg=You brought it to me. Thanks. 
