</newversion></questtextxml></bc2gt009a><evdonac02><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Deliver the Necklace debris to Explorer Ryn
desc=Hey there, wait a minute! I can feel it! With such a helping face you will support me, won't you? A girl of the Explorer Association found a huge necklace at the bottom of a cave during her cave exploration and now got cursed for that. Besides, very horrible&#x2026; the curse is letting money disappear! She told me the money disappears everyday even though she hides it carefully. To break the curse, you must find the pieces of the huge necklace and put them back together. The girl broke it in order to get away from the cave. The girl also has searched for the pieces here and there by herself, but she said it's too hard to search for those little pieces. Please collect the pieces. You can find them if you hunt down some monsters. In the end, you might get a reward from the girl.

NPC Position : Larksdowns - Hill of Sunrise
Target monsters : Strong Devil Walker, Devil Walker Harpooner, Toad, Mudfrog, Stone Lizard, Sick Treant
runDlg=The money is disappearing! It's horrible.
finishDlg=( Tears run down all over the explorer's face) Thank you! 
