desc=Now, we need the final ingredient. By using this an excellent dish might be completed! The ingredient is Firefrog's Hind Leg! Firefrog can be easily found around here. It's a very dangerous guy, but please take the risk so I can cook this fantastic food. I let you taste as much as you want, I'm begging you.
runDlg=This is the last! I promise. Please bring me Firefrog's Hind Leg!
finishDlg=Great! Now I am ready to make some fantastic food.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Collecting Lava Firefrog's Hind Leg
desc=Now, we need the final ingredient. By using this an excellent dish might be completed! The ingredient is Lava Firefrog's Hind Leg! Lava Firefrog can be easily found around here. It's a very dangerous guy, but please take the risk so I can cook this fantastic food. I let you taste as much as you want, I'm begging you.
runDlg=This is the last! I promise. Please bring me Lava Firefrog's Hind Leg!
finishDlg=Great! Now I am ready to make some fantastic food.
</newversion></questtextxml></nquest005><systuto02><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Delivering Dehydrated Food
desc=All our 'Dehydrated Food' is nearly gone, so I can't prepae much food. I'm afraid you can help me once again. You want to, but you don't know how to do so? I'll give you a recipe. If you collect the required materials and right-click on the 'Recipe' item, you'll have your dish. Are you ready to do it now? You can catch 'Filefish' and 'Anchovy' by fishing. You need to kill the following monsters to get 'Cinnamon': [Nananim, Cotton Mushroom, Dodo, Devil Walker] I'll be waiting for you. 
runDlg=In case you have consumed all your baits, you can purchase new ones from 'Tricia' in the northwest of the town. 
finishDlg=Thank you for your help. Do you understand how to make food? If you make food and eat it, some of your powers might be improved for a certain time. This is indeed very useful, so you should use the food often.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Delivering Dehydrated Food
