</newversion></questtextxml></classe002><classs004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Mark&#xC640; &#xB300;&#xD654;
desc=Mark, working eagerly in Roxbury, is surffering from stomach ache. There seems no doctor. Go to Mark and cure his stomach ache. After curing him, come back here. Here are a lot of patients to cure. 
runDlg=Ooh&#x2026;. Long time no see. Do you come here for help me? 
finishDlg=Uh? Pain's disappeared. Did you cure me?  Thank for this. When did you learn such a skill? Thank you anyway. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Conservation with Mark
desc=Mark, working eagerly in Roxbury, is surffering from stomach ache. There seems no doctor. Go to Mark and cure his stomach ache. After curing him, come back here. Here are a lot of patients to cure. 
runDlg=Ooh&#x2026;. Long time no see. Do you come here for help me? 
