desc=Emm, it's you. Last time you finished the Stone Guard thing without any problems. It seems that the rumors about you are true. That's great for us.

Anyway when you were hunting the Stone Guards, didn't you think their bodies are especially hard? I don't know how, probably they wear armors made of stones.

There is no problem with them since you got rid of them, but another monster appeared. Its appearance is similar with the Stone Guards, but it's said that it is much stronger. Some Mercenaries rushed to it and they all came back being attacked and knocked down, because their attack was futile. So before other weak guys are attacked, please go there and get rid of it. Life is precious.
runDlg=Please be a good example for other adventurers. Only you can do it. 
finishDlg=See this? Those guys ran into that monster and then escaped. When they look at you, their eyes are full of respect. 
