finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Hey, al i&#x15F;te, bu sana yard&#x131;mc&#x131; olacakt&#x131;r. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt02><tutostt03><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Delivery of the finished part to Stephen 
desc=Now, this is time to make a finished part. Make the finished part with the design and materials I gave you. Ouch! After making a finished part, the design will disappear because it is under a spell. So if  you want to make again, you'll be able to buy it again. Forget it.
runDlg=Are you finished with the stuff?
finishDlg=Good job. I'll confirm if it is good or not. 
 It's good. Here it is.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Tamamlanan par&#xE7;an&#x131;n Stephen'a teslim edilmesi
desc=&#x15E;imdi, ilk par&#xE7;ay&#x131; bitirmenin vakti geldi. Bu par&#xE7;ay&#x131; sana verdi&#x11F;im tasar&#x131;m ve de malzemeleri kullanarak tamamla. Ah! Bitirdikten sonra tasar&#x131;m ortadan kaybolacak &#xE7;&#xFC;nk&#xFC; &#xFC;zerinde bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC; var. Yani e&#x11F;er onu bir daha yapmak istersen, yeniden sat&#x131;n almak zorundas&#x131;n. Bunu asla unutma.
runDlg=&#x130;&#x15F;i bitirebildin mi?
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. &#x130;yi yapabilmi&#x15F; misin diye kontrol edece&#x11F;im. 
 San&#x131;r&#x131;m iyi. Al bakal&#x131;m.
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt03><tutostt04><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Elimination of Seeker Mole 
desc=Now, let's try to make another part. I confirmed the place that there are materials required in the making of a warship. Seeker Moles have a lot. Of course, other moles have a lot but Seeker moles have much more materials. So you'd better eliminate Seeker Mole and search through. Hurry up and bring the material. The taste of making a warship is started from now. 
runDlg=Did you collect a lot of materials? 
finishDlg=Good job. If the materials is deficient, collect them after eliminating Seeker moles. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Seeker Mole'un yok edilmesi
desc=&#x15E;imdi yeni bir par&#xE7;a yapal&#x131;m hadi. Bir sava&#x15F; gemisi yap&#x131;m&#x131; i&#xE7;in gerekli olan malzemelerin oldu&#x11F;u bir yer buldum. Seeker Mole'larda arad&#x131;klar&#x131;m&#x131;zdan &#xE7;ok fazla var. Ama elbette di&#x11F;er k&#xF6;stebeklerde de &#xE7;ok var ama Seeker mole'lar daha &#xE7;ok malzemeye sahipler. &#x130;&#x15F;te bu y&#xFC;zden sen en iyisi Seeker Mole'u yok edip onlardan arama yap. Acele et ve malzemeyi buraya getir. Sava&#x15F; gemisi yapman&#x131;n tad&#x131; &#xE7;&#x131;kmaya ba&#x15F;lad&#x131;. 
runDlg=&#xC7;ok malzeme toplad&#x131;n m&#x131;? 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. E&#x11F;er malzemeler eksik gelirse, daha &#xE7;ok Seeker Mole yok ederek tamamlars&#x131;n art&#x131;k. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt04><tutostt05><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Eliminate Weak Black Kimukeu
desc=I'll give you a task with experimenting the warship's force and sea sightseeing. Weak Black Kimukeus are living in the offing of Cardiff island here. They don't become a great threat but are troublesome in sailing. Please eliminate Weak Black Kimukeus for our good sailing. 
runDlg=Do you like the warship? Ha, ha. Okay, let's have a fun with it. 
finishDlg=Good job. They were troublesome to residents who use ships. Thanks to this job, we don't have anything to worry about. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Weak Black Kimukeu'yu yok et
desc=Denize a&#xE7;&#x131;l&#x131;p etraf&#x131; g&#xF6;rmen ve de sava&#x15F; gemisinin kuvvetini s&#x131;naman i&#xE7;in sana bir g&#xF6;rev verece&#x11F;im. Weak Black Kimukeus denen yarat&#x131;klar Cardiff Adas&#x131;'n&#x131;n a&#xE7;&#x131;klar&#x131;nda ya&#x15F;&#x131;yorlar. &#xC7;ok b&#xFC;y&#xFC;k bir tehdit olu&#x15F;turmuyorlar ancak denize a&#xE7;&#x131;ld&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;nda ba&#x15F;&#x131;na bela olabiliyorlar. Denizcili&#x11F;in iyili&#x11F;i i&#xE7;in l&#xFC;tfen Weak Black Kimukeus'lar&#x131; ortadan kald&#x131;r. 
runDlg=Sava&#x15F; gemisini be&#x11F;endin mi? Ha, ha. Tamam, o halde onunla biraz e&#x11F;lenelim. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. Gemi kullanan yerlilere sorun &#xE7;&#x131;kar&#x131;yorlard&#x131;.  Te&#x15F;ekk&#xFC;rler, art&#x131;k endi&#x15F;e etmemize gerek kalmad&#x131;. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt05><tutostt06><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=The destruction of Black Dragon Old Scoutship 
desc=Your skill got better a little. So I'll give you next task. Don't you want to do another thing with the stronger warship? The next target is to destroy Black Dragon Old Scoutship. Black Dragons have come around here and they seems to reconnoiter Cardiff island. Give a lesson to Black Dragon with the force of the warship. 
runDlg=Now, show the force of a new part to them. 
finishDlg=Good job. It was not a difficult job, is it? 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Black Dragon Old Scoutship'in yok edilmesi
desc=Yetene&#x11F;in biraz artt&#x131;. Bu y&#xFC;zden sana s&#x131;radaki g&#xF6;revi verece&#x11F;im. Daha g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; bir gemiyle yeni bir i&#x15F;e &#xE7;&#x131;kmak istemez miydin? S&#x131;radaki hedef Black Dragon Old Scoutship'i yok etmek. Black Dragon'lar bu civarlara geldiler ve g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;&#x15F;e bak&#x131;l&#x131;rsa Cardiff Island'da ke&#x15F;if yapmak, buray&#x131; incelemek istiyorlar. Bu sava&#x15F; gemisinin kuvvetiyle Black Dragon'lara bir ders ver. 
runDlg=&#x15E;imdi git ve onlara yeni tasar&#x131;m&#x131;n g&#xFC;c&#xFC;n&#xFC; g&#xF6;ster. 
finishDlg=Good job. It was not difficult, was it? 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt06><tutostt07><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Eliminate Strong Kimukeu
desc=Hey, you look like a true sailor. I think you are fit for the request that I got. The request need the man who went to sea somewhat. Did you stand against Kimukeus once? They brought their group. They look like stronger Kimukeu. Go and eliminate Strong Kimukeus. Well, I take responsibility about the reward. You don't need to worry about it. Now, play with Kimukeus cheerfully. 
runDlg=Is the ship safe? Well, it is strongly repaired. I think it won't be easily destroyed by Kimukeus' attack. 
finishDlg=Good job. Here is the reward. Ah! Wait a minute. I discovered a new thing again. Let's talk again after a wihile. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Strong Kimukeu'yu yok et
desc=Hey, ger&#xE7;ek bir denizci gibi g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yorsun. San&#x131;r&#x131;m senden isteyece&#x11F;im &#x15F;eyi yapmaya uygunsun. Bu g&#xF6;revde bir &#x15F;ekilde denize a&#xE7;&#x131;lm&#x131;&#x15F; biri gerekiyor. Sen daha &#xF6;nce Kimukeus'larla kar&#x15F;&#x131;la&#x15F;t&#x131;n, de&#x11F;il mi? &#x15E;imdi yeni bir birlikleri var ve daha g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; Kimukeu'lar gibi g&#xF6;r&#xFC;n&#xFC;yorlar.  Git ve Strong Kimukeus'lar&#x131; yok et.  &#xD6;d&#xFC;l&#xFC;n&#xFC;n sorumlulu&#x11F;unu ben al&#x131;yorum. O konuda endi&#x15F;elenme. &#x15E;imdi, git ve Kimukeus'larla e&#x11F;len bakal&#x131;m. 
runDlg=Gemi g&#xFC;vende mi? Eh ne de olsa &#xE7;ok g&#xFC;&#xE7;l&#xFC; bir &#x15F;ekilde yenilendi. San&#x131;r&#x131;m bir Kimukeus sald&#x131;r&#x131;s&#x131;ndan kolay kolay zarar g&#xF6;rmezdi. 
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. &#x130;&#x15F;te &#xF6;d&#xFC;l&#xFC;n. Ah! Bir dakika bekle. Yeni bir &#x15F;ey ke&#x15F;fettim yine. Bir s&#xFC;re sonra yeniden konu&#x15F;al&#x131;m. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt07><tutostt08><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Bringing [Design : Improved Pedrero Lv2]
desc=You're falling in the warship improvement. As I said before, I found a new design.  I am selling this. The price is low for you. Buy it and show me. Ah! I didn't say the name. It is written like this, Design : Improved Pedrero Lv2. 
runDlg=You'll find soon if you search carefully. 
finishDlg=Yeah, you bring it successfully. I'll confirm what materials are in here. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=[Design : Improved Pedrero Lv2] getirme
desc=Sava&#x15F; gemisi geli&#x15F;tirme i&#x15F;ine iyice al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;n. Sana daha &#xF6;nce de s&#xF6;yledi&#x11F;im gibi, yeni bir tasar&#x131;m buldum. Bunu sat&#x131;yorum. Senin i&#xE7;in fiyat&#x131; d&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;k tutar&#x131;m. Sat&#x131;n al ve bana g&#xF6;ster. Ah! &#x130;smini s&#xF6;ylemedim, i&#x15F;te bu: Design : Improved Pedrero Lv2. 
runDlg=E&#x11F;er dikkatlice ararsan onu &#xE7;ok yak&#x131;nda bulursun. 
finishDlg=Evet, ba&#x15F;ar&#x131;yla buldun. Burada gerekli olan malzemeleri onaylayaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt08><tutostt09><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Delivery of Improved Pedrero Lv2 to stephen 
desc=For making Improved Pedrero Lv2, two Grade 3 Iron and a Improved Pedrero Lv1 are required. it is not easy to fine Grade 3 Iron. 
 Do you remember the hunting of Seeker Moles? Perhaps we can find the iron collected at that time. If not, search their pocket. Then you'll be able to find it. 
runDlg=Not yet? Take you time. I'll wait until you finish. 
finishDlg=Good job. Here it is. It is better than I thought. Now only special parts remain. Keep trying. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Improved Pedrero Lv2'nin Stephen'a teslim edilmesi 
desc=Improved Pedrero Lv2 yapmak i&#xE7;in iki adet Grade 3 Iron ve bir de  Improved Pedrero Lv1 gerekiyor.  Grade 3 Iron bulmak kolay de&#x11F;ildir. 
 Seeker Mole av&#x131;n&#x131; hat&#x131;rl&#x131;yor musun? Belki de o zaman toplanan demiri bulabiliriz. E&#x11F;er olmazsa da ceplerini ara. O zaman bulacaks&#x131;n. 
runDlg=Daha olmad&#x131; m&#x131;? Acele etme. Sen bitirene kadar ben beklerim.  
finishDlg=&#x130;yi i&#x15F; &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;n. &#x130;&#x15F;te burada. D&#xFC;&#x15F;&#xFC;nd&#xFC;&#x11F;&#xFC;mden de iyi. &#x15E;imdi sadece &#xF6;zel par&#xE7;alar kald&#x131;. Denemeye devam. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt09><tutostt10><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Conversation with Ash 
desc=You made an effort. This is the last I can do. Now you should remodel the warship with only your effort. Try to make the best warship. 
 Ah, I almost forgot. I already said that Ash would give a design for reward you have supported me. Take it from Ash. 
 Haha! It is not expensive. Be easy about it. 
runDlg=It is not expensive. So you don't need to be uncomfortable. 
finishDlg=You came here! This is the thing that Stephen asked I'd give you. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Ash ile sohbet 
desc=&#xC7;aba g&#xF6;sterdin. Bu, senin i&#xE7;in yapabilece&#x11F;im son &#x15F;ey. &#x15E;imdi sava&#x15F; gemisine yeni modelini kendi ba&#x15F;&#x131;na vermelisin. En iyi sava&#x15F; gemisini yapmaya &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;. 
 Ah, az kals&#x131;n unutuyordum. Bana &#xE7;ok yard&#x131;mc&#x131; oldu&#x11F;un i&#xE7;in Ash'ten sana &#xF6;d&#xFC;l olarak bir tasar&#x131;m vermesini rica ettim. Git ve Ash'ten al. 
 Haha! Pahal&#x131; de&#x11F;il. O kadar takma kafana. 
runDlg=Pahal&#x131; bir &#x15F;ey de&#x11F;il. Rahats&#x131;z olmana gerek yok. 
finishDlg=Geldin demek! &#x130;&#x15F;te Stephen'&#x131;n sana vermemi s&#xF6;yledi&#x11F;i tasar&#x131;m. 
</newversion></questtextxml></tutostt10><fusion001><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lionel 
desc=Come right in. These days it is very difficult to operate my store. But Sir Lionel has operated the territory. Isn't it amazing? 
 You have wondered, haven't you? Is there a gold mine in Cardiff island?
.......
 Hoho! It's just a joke. If there is a gold mine, the explorer association would have declared.
 How about you? You also wonder, right? You are an explore from outside. So Sir Lionel maybe let you know it! Please confirm it instead of me. Sir Lionel lives in the mansion, located the north of Roxbury. 
 In case of knowing the secret, please let me know. 
runDlg=Rich explorers leaves to other islands more and more. As time goes by, it's more difficult to operate my store. 
finishDlg=Ouch! Another explorer was fooled by Miss. Rosemary. She continues to habitually use the joke in drink.
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Lionel ile sohbet
desc=Gel i&#xE7;eri. Bug&#xFC;nlerde d&#xFC;kkan&#x131;m&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;rmam epey zor. Ama Sir Lionel it&#xFC;m b&#xF6;lgeyi y&#xF6;netiyor, &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;r&#x131;yor. Bu harika de&#x11F;il mi? 
 Merak ettin de&#x11F;il mi? You have wondered, haven't you? Cardiff adas&#x131;nda bir alt&#x131;n madeni var m&#x131;?  
.....
 Hoho! Bu sadece bir &#x15F;aka. E&#x11F;er bir alt&#x131;n madeni varsa ka&#x15F;ifler birli&#x11F;i bunu a&#xE7;&#x131;klard&#x131;. 
 Sen ne diyorsun? Sen de merak ettin &#xF6;yle de&#x11F;il mi? Sen d&#x131;&#x15F;ar&#x131;dan gelen bir ka&#x15F;ifsin. Bu y&#xFC;zden belki de So Sir Lionel sana s&#xF6;yler! L&#xFC;tfen bunu benim yerime do&#x11F;rula. Sir Lionel  Roxbury'nin kuzeyinde bir konakta ya&#x15F;&#x131;yor. 
 E&#x11F;er s&#x131;rr&#x131; &#xF6;&#x11F;renecek olursan l&#xFC;tfen bana da haber ver. 
runDlg=Zengin ka&#x15F;ifler di&#x11F;er adalara gitmeye ba&#x15F;lad&#x131;lar. Zaman ge&#xE7;tik&#xE7;e d&#xFC;kkan&#x131;m&#x131; &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;rmam da zorla&#x15F;&#x131;yor. 
finishDlg=Eyvah! Bir ba&#x15F;ka ka&#x15F;if daha Miss. Rosemary taraf&#x131;ndan kand&#x131;r&#x131;ld&#x131;. Her sarho&#x15F; oldu&#x11F;unda bu &#x15F;akay&#x131; yapar.
</newversion></questtextxml></fusion001><fusion002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Elimination of Nanani 
desc=All right, I guess you came here to confirm the operating expenses of the territory. I'll add your name on the list of explorers who Miss. Rosemary sent. Well, it is not a perfect secret. It is just operated by the tax that residents pay and operating expenses from the kingdom. 
 Haha. what the heck is your look? Are you despondent? 
 After seeing your look, I can't help talking about the reason that Rosemary sent you to me. In fact there is another source of income in addition to the tax and support fund from the kingdom. Do you know about option fusion? 
 It's difficult to explain option fusion but I'll let you know if you receive my request. Miss Rosemary 
 It is not a difficult request. The number of Nanani on the Weedridge has surged. They are troublesome. Please, Get rid of Nanani. 
runDlg=I'll let you know the reason why Rosemary sent you to me after finishing the mission. 
finishDlg=The sound Nanani make is very loud every night! Now I can sleep quietly. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Nanani'nin yok edilmesi 
desc=Tamam, san&#x131;yorum buraya b&#xF6;lgenin y&#xF6;netim masraflar&#x131;n&#x131;n nas&#x131;l kar&#x15F;&#x131;land&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; &#xF6;&#x11F;renmeye geldin. Miss Rosemarry'nin yollad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; ka&#x15F;ifler listesine ad&#x131;n&#x131; ekleyece&#x11F;im. Eh, asl&#x131;nda muhte&#x15F;em bir s&#x131;r de&#x11F;il bu. Burada ya&#x15F;ayanlar&#x131;n &#xF6;dedi&#x11F;i vergiler ve krall&#x131;ktan y&#xF6;netim masraflar&#x131; i&#xE7;in gelenlerle y&#xF6;netiyoruz. 
 Haha. Bu bak&#x131;&#x15F; da neyin nesi b&#xF6;yle? Hayal k&#x131;r&#x131;kl&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;na m&#x131; u&#x11F;rad&#x131;n? 
 Surat&#x131;n&#x131; g&#xF6;rd&#xFC;kten sonra Rosemary'nin seni neden bana yollad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; hakk&#x131;nda konu&#x15F;madan duramayaca&#x11F;&#x131;m. Asl&#x131;na bakarsan, krall&#x131;ktan gelen destek ve vergiler d&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;nda ba&#x15F;ka bir kaynak da var. Option fusion nedir bilir misin? 
 Bunu a&#xE7;&#x131;klamak zor ama e&#x11F;er g&#xF6;revimi kabul edersen sana option fusion'dan bahsedebilirim. 
 &#xC7;ok zor bir g&#xF6;rev de&#x11F;il. Weedridge'deki Nanani say&#x131;s&#x131; artt&#x131;. Sorun &#xE7;&#x131;kar&#x131;yorlar. L&#xFC;tfen bu Nanani'den kurtul. 
runDlg=G&#xF6;revi tamamlad&#x131;ktan sonra  Rosemary'nin neden seni bana yollad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n&#x131; anlataca&#x11F;&#x131;m. 
finishDlg=Nanani'nin gece &#xE7;&#x131;kard&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131; sesler &#xE7;ok y&#xFC;ksekti! Ama art&#x131;k sessizlik i&#xE7;inde uyuyabilece&#x11F;im.  
</newversion></questtextxml></fusion002><fusion003><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Collecting Tough Wild Boar's tooth 
Mission2=Collecting Mushroom Leader's tooth 
desc=You did my favor. So I answer your curiosity. In fact option fusion is not a sort of secret. All knows about it  except a beginner explorer like you. 
 Option fusion is ancient magic in brief. If this magic is used, a special power is created at a thing. I don't know about more detailed thing. The kingdom continues to study, but it is just a incomplete magic. 
 The lord of each island have actually a capability for option fusion. After being promised the lords would keep their oath, the kingdom let them know. 
 Option fusion has difficulties in using it and many materials are required for magic. Um.... I had you help. So if you bring the materials, I'll show option fusion one time. The materials are Tough Wild Boar's tooth and Mushroom Leader's tooth. Go bring them if you have time. 
runDlg=I made a tongueslip to Rosemary in drink. If she indroduce a new explorer to me, I said buying liquor. 
finishDlg=Haha. You bring it hurriedly. I guess you are interested in the ancient magic. 
 I need more time to make magic articles with the materials. Come back after a while. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Tough Wild Boar's tooth toplama
Mission2=Mushroom Leader's tooth toplama
desc=Bana bu iyili&#x11F;i yapt&#x131;n, ben de senin merak&#x131;n&#x131; giderece&#x11F;im. Asl&#x131;nda option fusion bir s&#x131;r de&#x11F;il. Senin gibi yeni ba&#x15F;layan bir ka&#x15F;if d&#x131;&#x15F;&#x131;nda herkes bunun ne oldu&#x11F;unu bilir. 
 Option fusion k&#x131;saca eski bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC;d&#xFC;r. Bu b&#xFC;y&#xFC; kullan&#x131;l&#x131;rsa &#xF6;zel bir g&#xFC;&#xE7; yarat&#x131;lm&#x131;&#x15F; olur. Daha fazla ayr&#x131;nt&#x131;dan haberim yok. Krall&#x131;k bu konuda &#xE7;al&#x131;&#x15F;maya devam ediyor ama bu, tamamlanmam&#x131;&#x15F; bir b&#xFC;y&#xFC;. 
 Her adan&#x131;n Lordu option fusion konusunda bir beceriye sahip. Lordlar s&#xF6;zlerini tutacaklar&#x131;na yemin ettikten sonra Krall&#x131;k onlara a&#xE7;&#x131;klama yapt&#x131;. 
 Option fusion'&#x131;n kullan&#x131;m&#x131;nda zorluklar var ve bu b&#xFC;y&#xFC; i&#xE7;in pek &#xE7;ok malzeme gerekiyor. H&#x131;mm .... Yard&#x131;m etmene izin verece&#x11F;im. E&#x11F;er bana malzemeleri getirirsen, sana option fusion'&#x131; bir kez g&#xF6;sterece&#x11F;im. Malzemeler &#x15F;unlar: Tough Wild Boar's tooth ve Mushroom Leader's tooth. Bunlar&#x131; bana getir, e&#x11F;er vaktin varsa. 
runDlg=&#x130;&#xE7;erken Rosemary'ye a&#x11F;z&#x131;mdan ka&#xE7;&#x131;rd&#x131;m. Beni yeni bir ka&#x15F;ifle tan&#x131;&#x15F;t&#x131;rd&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;nda neden bu kadar i&#xE7;tim diye hep soruyorum kendime... 
finishDlg=Haha. &#xC7;ok &#xE7;abuk getirdin. San&#x131;yorum ki eski b&#xFC;y&#xFC;lerle ilgilisin.  
 Bu malzemelerle b&#xFC;y&#xFC; maddeleri yapabilmek i&#xE7;in daha fazla zamana ihtiyac&#x131;m var. 
</newversion></questtextxml></fusion003><fusion004><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Conversation with Lionel 
desc=Like explaining you, option fusion is not complete. Um, do you wonder if it is incomplete in a point? 
 The magic in the front of this old book was already broken and can give a special capability at a thing. But its lasting time is not long. Perhaps there seems to be the skill in the back of the book. The break of old book is not easy. 
 Do you immediately see the magic? Haha. If I don't have an important job, you can come here whenever you want. 
 Oh! I forgot a word for you. 
 We get some Gelt for using option fusion.  I want you to understand. It is the rule from the kingdom. But it is not much. 
finishDlg=Haha. You seem to be impetuous more than thought. Wellcome if you prepare your ability and Gelt. 
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Lionel ile sohbet 
desc=Sana a&#xE7;&#x131;klad&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;m gibi, option fusion hen&#xFC;z tamamlanm&#x131;&#x15F; de&#x11F;il. Hangi noktada eksik oldu&#x11F;unu merak ediyor musun? 
 Bu eski kitab&#x131;n ba&#x15F;&#x131;ndaki b&#xFC;y&#xFC; &#xE7;oktan bozuldu ve sana &#xF6;zel bir beceri kazand&#x131;rabilir. Ama etkisi &#xE7;ok s&#xFC;rm&#xFC;yor. Belki de kitab&#x131;n arka taraf&#x131;nda daha iyi bir yetenek vard&#x131;r. Bu kitab&#x131;n de&#x15F;ifre edilmesi kolay de&#x11F;il. 
 B&#xFC;y&#xFC;y&#xFC; hemen mi g&#xF6;rmek istiyorsun? Haha. E&#x11F;er &#xF6;nemli bir i&#x15F;im olmasa, buraya istedi&#x11F;in zaman gelebilirsin derdim. 
 Oh! Bahsetmeyi unuttum. 
 Option fusion kullanmak i&#xE7;in Gelt al&#x131;yoruz. Bunu anlaman&#x131; isterim. Bu, krall&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;n koydu&#x11F;u bir kural. Ama merak etme, &#xE7;ok Gelt istemiyoruz. 
finishDlg=Haha. Sand&#x131;&#x11F;&#x131;mdan da tez canl&#x131;ym&#x131;&#x15F;s&#x131;n. Becerini ve Gelt'ini haz&#x131;rlad&#x131;ysan buyurabilirsin. 
</newversion></questtextxml></fusion004></diff><new><evxmas001> evxmas001</evxmas001><evxmas002> evxmas002</evxmas002><evxmas003> evxmas003</evxmas003><evxmas004> evxmas004</evxmas004></new><settings><searchkey> questlistid</searchkey><ignore> id</ignore><columnnametable> </columnnametable><parsexml> </parsexml></settings></server_questtext_TR></number71></sql></Cache>
